OL,3,CFarnham v Miles: Could this be the
OL,4,Cbattle for Chief Minister?
OL,6,FAs the dust settles on Jersey's
OL,7,Felection, could it be a straight race
OL,8,Fbetween incumbent Chief Minister
OL,9,FLyndon Farnham and poll-topper Helen
OL,10,FMiles for the top job?
OL,12,FMr Farnham has already made it clear
OL,13,Fthat he would like to continue in the
OL,14,Frole after emerging as the third-most
OL,15,Fpopular candidate for Senator, 1,642
OL,16,Fvotes behind Dr Miles.
OL,18,FDr Miles has previously served as
OL,19,FJustice and Home Affairs Minister and
OL,20,Fis thought to be interested in the
OL,21,Fposition.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
