OL,3,CFarnham v Miles: Could this be the
OL,4,Cbattle for Chief Minister?
OL,6,FFollowing the results, she told ITV
OL,7,FChannel that she was feeling "very
OL,8,Fhappy" and "still very surprised" at
OL,9,Ftopping the Senatorial poll.
OL,11,FWhen asked directly whether she would
OL,12,Fput herself forward, she said that she
OL,13,F"wouldn't rule it out".
OL,15,FBefore the election, several other
OL,16,Fcandidates were thought to be
OL,17,Fconsidering a run.
