OL,3,CFarnham v Miles: Could this be the
OL,4,Cbattle for Chief Minister?
OL,6,FITV News understands Dr Miles and
OL,7,Ffellow Senator-Elect Elaine Millar
OL,8,Fagreed that whoever had the strongest
OL,9,Fmandate between them would run against
OL,10,FFarnham, while Senator-Elect Ian Gorst
OL,11,Fcould also throw his hat in the ring.
OL,13,FMr Farnham has served as Chief
OL,14,FMinister since 2024, following a vote
OL,15,Fof no-confidence in Kristina Moore.
OL,17,FAny States Assembly member with six
OL,18,Fbackers can put themselves forward for
OL,19,Fthe position and must submit their
OL,20,Fnominations by 5pm on Thursday 11 June.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
