OL,3,CFarnham v Miles: Could this be the
OL,4,Cbattle for Chief Minister?
OL,6,FNew members will officially be sworn
OL,7,Fin on Friday 12 June and the Chief
OL,8,FMinister will be selected a week
OL,9,Flater, on Friday 19 June.
OL,11,FA vote will be held in the Assembly
OL,12,Fand, if no candidate secures a
OL,13,Fmajority in the first round, the
OL,14,Fperson with the fewest number of votes
OL,15,Fwill be eliminated and the process
OL,16,Fwill be repeated until a winner is
OL,17,Ffound.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
