OL,3,CFarnham v Miles: Could this be the
OL,4,Cbattle for Chief Minister?
OL,6,FMinisters will then be selected by
OL,7,FStates Members on Friday 26 June,
OL,8,Fthrough a similar vote process, and
OL,9,Fformally appointed on Monday 29 June.
OL,11,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,12,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,13,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,14,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,15,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,16,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,17,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,18,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,19,FThursday...
